headline: Fiserv and COCC Meet Tomorrow’s Digital Banking Expectations
summary: MILWAUKEE, December 11, 2024--Fiserv, Inc. (NYSE: FI), a leading global provider of payments and financial services technology, today announced an expanded relationship with COCC, a client-owned fintech serving over 200 community banks and credit unions.
